      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 16:58:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长莱恩称通胀率重返 2% 目标尚无定论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/ecb-s-lane-says-return-to-2-inflation-target-isn-t-secure-yet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行首席经济学家菲利普·莱恩表示，欧洲央行让通胀率回升至 2% 的斗争尚未胜利，利率必须维持在必要的高位才能实现这一目标，同时又不能对经济造成过度损害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/ecb-s-lane-says-return-to-2-inflation-target-isn-t-secure-yet</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 16:52:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦电力公司警告称，故障将导致停电次数增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/zimbabwe-power-utility-warns-of-increased-blackouts-due-to-fault</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦国有电力公司表示，由于燃煤发电厂出现技术故障，该公司实施了加强限电措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/zimbabwe-power-utility-warns-of-increased-blackouts-due-to-fault</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 16:33:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其调查财务主管辞职的虚假社交媒体帖子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/turkey-probes-false-social-media-posts-that-finance-chief-quit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其资本市场委员会（SPK）周六宣布，土耳其正在调查社交媒体上错误宣称财政部长穆罕默德·西姆塞克已辞职的帖子，该帖子导致伊斯坦布尔证券交易所股价大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/turkey-probes-false-social-media-posts-that-finance-chief-quit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 09:27:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国不会禁止债券交易但认为购买狂潮存在风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/china-won-t-ban-bond-trading-but-sees-risk-in-buying-frenzy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国人民银行没有寻求、也不会寻求禁止合法的投资或交易其国债，但其认为大举购买这些证券存在风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/china-won-t-ban-bond-trading-but-sees-risk-in-buying-frenzy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 08:22:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀放缓，欧洲央行准备再次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/euro-zone-s-sinking-inflation-has-ecb-gearing-up-for-next-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行官员大谈下个月再次降息的前景，而通胀率将回落至目标水平的预测将给他们带来信心。]]></description>
